## 5️⃣ User Defined Function

```python
cities = ["delhi", "gurgaon", "noida", "pune", "mumbai", "chennai"]

heroes = ["thor", "ironman", "captain america", "shaktiman"]

def print_len(lst):
    print(len(lst))

print_len(cities)
print_len(heroes)
```

### Output
```text
6
4
```

