## 6️⃣ Factorial Without Function

```python
n = 5
fact = 1

for i in range(1, n + 1):
    fact *= i
    print(fact)
```

### Output
```text
1
2
6
24
120
```

---

## 7️⃣ Factorial Using Function

```python
def cal_fact(n):
    fact = 1

    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        fact *= i

    print(fact)

cal_fact(6)
```

### Output
```text
720
```

